{"type": "article", "id": 7457, "title": "Helena Franca 多用钟表", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-17T07:44:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234140Wg4mJo1XBrtKqjb3.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t设计师 Helena Franca 推出了两款外形相似到各有特色的钟表，表面皆采用激光切割亚克力玻璃制成。把手式钟表带有一个把手，可以方便移动，并且当钟表挂在墙上静止状态时，这个镂空的把手可以当作一个架子悬挂领带，眼镜等日常物品。而另外一款架子式钟表的底部带有一个透明架子，可以放置钥匙，手机，手表等随身携带的物品，以助于提醒你出门别忘了带这些必需品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234138yZ51pzTXnCleQL9D.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.50333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234138yv2Ocj6WLQ97wzeX.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.50166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052341380LJTbdpCqVPsUmgv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.31333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234139Gz0PFqgljvtbCoWa.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.25833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234139iwb08dxK2aGlzqcT.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.29\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}